{"title":"Dangerholm’s Scott Spark RC Visione Includes 3D Printed  Bar/Stem","link":"https://bikerumor.com/dangerholms-scott-spark-rc-visione-custom-bike/","date":1731604576000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full--1536x1024.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"Dangerholm's Scott Spark RC Visione full  \" /></p>\n<p>Mountain bike tech has made quantum leaps over the past 15 years; wireless shifting and nearly integrated everything. Sometimes, that progress come at the cost of aesthetics, and serviceability — but not this build. Custom beautification mad man Dangerholm takes sets his sights on the Scott Spark RC and reimagines it in Rosso Corsa elegance.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-close-up--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-close-up--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Dangerholm's Scott Spark RC Visione bar close up\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-close-up--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-close-up--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-close-up--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-close-up--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-close-up--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-close-up--2048x1366.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-close-up--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-close-up--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(<strong>All Photos:By Gustav Gullholm</strong>)<br /></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Dangerholm looks for inspiration in Italian sports cars to bridge those gaps in his latest creation, the Scott Spark RC Visione. This concept bike embodies where racing innovation, modern aesthetics, and practical design intersect. It showcases next-level integration with a nod to its Italian inspiration, which is highlighted in a stunning “Rosso Corsa” paint job reminiscent of Ferrari.</p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>“<em>The Italian name ‘Visione’ and the Ferrari ‘Rosso Corsa’ paint job is a small homage to the incredible concept cars, motorsport classics, and designs for which we have Italy to thank. A deep source of inspiration, for when you want to try and push the limits.”</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Dangerholm</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full-bike--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full-bike--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Dangerholm's Scott Spark RC Visione full bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full-bike--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full-bike--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full-bike--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full-bike--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full-bike--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full-bike--2048x1366.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full-bike--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full-bike--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Dangerholm — Scott Spark RC Visione</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p>From dropper posts to refined 1x drivetrains and updated geometries, mountain bikes today are built to maximize speed and control. But another wave of subtle, and equally performance enhancing changes is taking place: seamless integration of components that blend performance and aesthetics. The Spark RC Visione isn’t just about eye-catching design—it’s a complete rethink of user-focused integration, made possible by state-of-the-art 3D printing (and wood).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-wooden-bar--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-wooden-bar--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Dangerholm's Scott Spark RC Visione wooden bar\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-wooden-bar--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-wooden-bar--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-wooden-bar--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-wooden-bar--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-wooden-bar--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-wooden-bar--2048x1366.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-wooden-bar--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-wooden-bar--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>3D-Printing and Wooden Prototypes</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>At the core of the Vision is an advanced 3D-printed handlebar, co-developed by Syncros and German manufacturing powerhouse <a href=\"https://www.trumpf.com/en_US/\">TRUMPF.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-compair-scaled-e1731428577267.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1322\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-compair-scaled-e1731428577267.webp\" alt=\"Dangerholm's Scott Spark RC Visione bar compair\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-compair-scaled-e1731428577267.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-compair-scaled-e1731428577267-297x192.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-compair-scaled-e1731428577267-1536x992.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-compair-scaled-e1731428577267-120x77.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bar-compair-scaled-e1731428577267-768x496.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This handlebar hides brake hoses with a snap-in channel design, eliminating the inconvenience of routing cables internally. While Syncros’ engineers, Maxime Lallemand, and Quentin Beauregard, executed the engineering finesse, the idea began with a wooden prototype—old-school creativity meeting cutting-edge technology.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-computer-mount--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-computer-mount--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Dangerholm's Scott Spark RC Visione computer mount\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-computer-mount--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-computer-mount--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-computer-mount--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-computer-mount--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-computer-mount--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-computer-mount--2048x1366.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-computer-mount--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-computer-mount--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>No Wires and Clean Lines </strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>With <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/rockshox-flight-attendant-2024/\">RockShox’s wireless Flight Attendant</a> system on board, mechanical suspension cables are a thing of the past. The bike leverages SRAM’s AXS tech, fine-tuned with <a href=\"https://www.zirbel.ch/en/\">ultra-minimalist Zirbel Twister</a> controllers tucked discreetly into the custom handlebar. There is no external clutter, just clean, precise shifting.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bars-close--scaled-e1731428329536.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1518\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bars-close--scaled-e1731428329536.webp\" alt=\"Dangerholm's Scott Spark RC Visione bars close\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bars-close--scaled-e1731428329536.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bars-close--scaled-e1731428329536-297x220.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bars-close--scaled-e1731428329536-1536x1139.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bars-close--scaled-e1731428329536-120x89.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bars-close--scaled-e1731428329536-768x569.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Advanced Manufacturing for Ride-Ready Components</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>TRUMPF’s 3D printing prowess enabled the manufacture of this lightweight 6061 aluminum handlebar with complex shapes that were impossible through traditional methods.  </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>The result?</em> A fully certified, ISO-tested component that’s ready for real-world trails.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bars--scaled-e1731428382859.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1412\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bars--scaled-e1731428382859.webp\" alt=\"Dangerholm's Scott Spark RC Visione bars\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bars--scaled-e1731428382859.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bars--scaled-e1731428382859-297x205.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bars--scaled-e1731428382859-1536x1059.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bars--scaled-e1731428382859-120x83.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-bars--scaled-e1731428382859-768x530.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Drool-Worthy Spec</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Spark RC Visione doesn’t just look the part—it’s built to race. Equipped with SRAM’s XX SL Eagle Transmission and tuned with a <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/ceramicspeed-ospw-rs/\">CeramicSpeed OSPW</a> cage and bottom bracket, the drivetrain is set for maximum efficiency. Trickstuff Piccola manages braking with custom 3D-printed titanium levers, showcasing both performance and cutting-edge aesthetics. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/zipp-1zero-hi-top-carbon-xc-wheels/\">Zipp 1ZERO HiTop</a> SW wheels complete the setup, blending durability and compliance for technical trails.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Dangerholm's Scott Spark RC Visione full  \" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full--297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full--1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full--120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full--768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full--2048x1366.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full--800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Dangerholms-Scott-Spark-RC-Visione-full--720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2><strong>Dangerholm’s SCOTT Spark RC Visione</strong> – Build Details </h2>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Frame</strong>: SCOTT Spark RC size L</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Thru axles</strong>: METI Titanium</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Rear shock</strong>: RockShox SID Flight Attendant</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Fork</strong>: RockShox SID Ultimate Flight Attendant</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Headset</strong>: Syncros adjustable HA with CeramicSpeed SLT bearings</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Handlebar</strong>: Syncros x TRUMPF x Dangerholm 3D printed prototype</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Grips</strong>: Syncros Foam Grips</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Garmin mount</strong>: Syncros iC Front Computer Mount</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Seat post</strong>: RockShox Reverb AXS 100mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Saddle</strong>: Bike Ahead Composites Hyper Saddle</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Controllers</strong>: Zirbel Twister WE01 with custom SRAM AXS BlipBox</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Brakes</strong>: Trickstuff Piccola with TRUMPF 3D-printed titanium levers</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Brake caliper bolts</strong>: METI Titanium</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Brake rotors</strong>: Trickstuff Dächle UL (160mm &amp; 180mm)</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Rear derailleur</strong>: SRAM XX SL Eagle Transmission</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Rear derailleur cage</strong>: CeramicSpeed X OSPW for Transmission</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Crankarms</strong>: 5Dev XC titanium</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Power meter</strong>: SRAM XX SL 38T</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Pedals</strong>: Xpedo M-Force 8 Ti</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Bottom bracket</strong>: CeramicSpeed DUB</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Chain</strong>: SRAM XX SL Eagle Transmission</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Cassette</strong>: SRAM XX SL Eagle Transmission</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Wheels</strong>: Zipp 1ZERO HiTop SW</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Tires</strong>: Vittoria Mezcal and Peyote XC Race 2.4”</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Sealant</strong>: Syncros Eco Sealant</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Bottle cages</strong>: Geek Components 3D-printed titanium, Syncros Tailor Cage 1.0 as an alternative</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Bike computer</strong>: Hammerhead Karoo</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Weight</strong>: 11.02kg / 24.29lbs (including pedals)</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>With the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/tag/scott-spark-rc-processed/\">Scott Spark RC</a> Visione, Dangerholm sets the bar high for what’s possible in integration and user-friendly innovation. Expect this evolution to become the norm as tech-savvy riders and super-mechanics push the envelope of whats possible. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>For the detailed spec list and more, check out <a href=\"https://www.scott-sports.com/us/en/\">Scott-sports.com</a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/dangerholms-scott-spark-rc-visione-custom-bike/\">Dangerholm’s Scott Spark RC Visione Includes 3D Printed  Bar/Stem</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jordan Villella","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"0a41a238fe5900ef1779868ada7da7b2682311a63a411d345ceb591db9d28224","category":"Cycling"}